com.gwtplatform.dispatch.rest.client

Class AbstractRestAction<R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.rest.client.AbstractRestAction<R>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - the result type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    RestAction<R>, HasSecured, TypedAction<R>

    public abstract class AbstractRestAction<R>
extends Object
implements RestAction<R>
    Provides a basic implementation of RestAction to inheritors. This is used by GWTP code-generator to create the actions defined by the services.
